articles.author: Ewan Palmer
articles.title: California Coronavirus Case Confirmed in Patient Who Traveled to Orange County From Wuhan
articles.description: The infected person in Orange County is the third confirmed case of the illness in the U.S. so far as the global death toll reaches 56.
articles.content:
Officials in California confirmed that a person in Orange County, California, has tested positive for the novel coronavirus.
